{"tid":2027540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我迫不及待想玩玩了","createTime":"2020-05-21T12:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T13:11:09.000Z","uid":30213,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"06e5b8b7aac65ad4a884a405885b4969970889b7","tid":2027540,"uid":30213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:09:06.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和中國接軌，<br />\n接軌後要拼盡全力讚黨，拿取權力。&nbsp;<br />\n會首先經香港公安局進場，先打死幾個暴徒。&nbsp;<br />\n然後一邊殺人一邊強姦，以最快速度上位。&nbsp;<br />\n成功KO真點香港人後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。&nbsp;<br />\n(搞黨媒，養紅軍，小粉紅，去幫有需要的新移民)&nbsp;<br />\n4年國安法，將來就可以用法律監管香港所有異見份子，黃店。&nbsp;<br />\n又要負責幫全港機構和香港政府，同中共聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為中共制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入黨。&nbsp;<br />\n簡直是共產黨主力核心。&nbsp;<br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f05991687d9ef302676373f47bbbe6f493782ab","tid":2027540,"uid":30213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"快啲下載VPN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e56d8f41fb801ce2b15d630e0c7f593196307ff","tid":2027540,"uid":205221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRon5sw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRon5sw.jpg&h=5aa4d66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280b5bb239e527269cc55f21c3550bb324dc6aeb","tid":2027540,"uid":32454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:24:49.000Z","msg":"我係中國人啊HI!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f48fce5e6d33025fb4a68b1bd8ff23d543e728","tid":2027540,"uid":58242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"280b5bb239e527269cc55f21c3550bb324dc6aeb","tid":202